{"type":null,"faqId":7115,"title":"如何通过蓝牙传输文件？","answer":"开启蓝牙并连接成功：在<strong>主菜单</strong>进入<strong>&ldquo;设置&rdquo;</strong>界面，选择<strong>&ldquo;无线和网络&rdquo;,</strong>勾选<strong>&ldquo;蓝牙&rdquo;</strong>为开启，进入<strong>&ldquo;蓝牙设置&rdquo;,</strong>勾选<strong>&ldquo;可检测性&rdquo;(</strong>可以被对方检测到本机的蓝牙设备），从扫描到的<strong>&ldquo;蓝牙设备&rdquo;</strong>列表中选择要配对的对象进行配对，配对成功后可以进行文件传输。<br />音乐传输：进入<strong>&ldquo;</strong>音乐播放器<strong>&rdquo;</strong>或<strong>&ldquo;</strong>媒体库<strong>&rdquo;</strong>选择<strong>任意要发送的文件长按</strong>-&gt;<strong>共享</strong>-&gt;<strong>蓝牙</strong>，即可传输文件。<br />保存位置：<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>文件管理器</strong>，通过蓝牙传输的文件在<strong>bluetooth</strong>文件夹下。","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7255","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1313738397000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":337,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":13,"times":4,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.3,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}